>\n<br />\n對象：18歲以上、香港永久性居民<br />\n<br />\n語言：繁體中文<br />\n<br />\n時長：10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n內容：問卷可分為四部分<br />\n<br />\n一）對香港現況的看法<br />\n二）情緒健康與政治參與<br />\n三）對社會上不同群體的看法<br />\n四）背景資料<br />\n<br />\n問卷連結：<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/cuhkpsychpoll\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fcuhkpsychpoll&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8rvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=0203fa40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/cuhkpsychpoll</a> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n是項研究資料絕對保密，唯相關研究團隊人員方可取閱。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n不論政治立場及政治參與程度，我們都誠邀你參與！<br />\n<br />\n如有疑問，請電3943-4168向謝先生、黃小姐或馮小姐查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n Anybody Can try try to fill in this questionnaire"},{"pid":"d1053a788d3a17d6bdd0ddfbdc0853a29b6f0944","tid":1582271,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f6ce2b8a8a0932be6484777760849b951d941b","tid":1582271,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb461b1cea5bcf7761d39891e0da8d5112036cc9","tid":1582271,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"訂咗蛋糕點先退到訂？"},{"pid":"1a1eff0985bcb51b7819330890a5ad7327dc04d3","tid":1582271,"uid":321906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T01:09:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf0311404a9c326658b8de8b6dda3b57dea86f2f","tid":1582271,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb461b1cea5bcf7761d39891e0da8d5112036cc9","tid":1582271,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"訂咗蛋糕點先退到訂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:28:02.000Z","msg":"唔知wor"},{"pid":"89281cffd39e24c4ab11b17acb7f94bf76e4f3f6","tid":1582271,"uid":314531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"r